---
title: Seared Salmon & Almond-Caper Sauce with Feta & Dill Potatoes
description: You're going to love this one – the texture of the almond-caper sauce against the succulent salmon is mind-blowingly good.  With aromatic dill sprinkled over roasted veggies, plus steamed broccolini, we reckon it's destined for greatness!
